milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (547) involving teams Australia & Pakistan in ODIs
Dean Jones and Steve Waugh's 173-run partnership is the highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 157 between Dean Jones and Robbie Kerr
Dean Jones and Steve Waugh's 173-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 157 between Dean Jones and Robbie Kerr
Wasim Akram and Asif Mujtaba's 43-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 41 between Ijaz Faqih and Rashid Khan
